          "displayName": "Prabhu Joseph",
          "active": true,
          "timeZone": "Etc/UTC"
        },
        "body": "Hi [~sunilg], In addition, we also need to include below code snippet in UserGroupMappingPlacementRule#getMappedQueue before returning the mapped queue, which will return a valid queue which is a existent leaf queue. \n\n{code}\n     for (QueueMapping mapping : mappings) {\n         if (queue == null || !(queue instanceof LeafQueue)) {\n                  continue;\n         }\n         return queue;\n    }\n{code}",
        "updateAuthor": {
          "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=prabhujoseph",
          "name": "prabhujoseph",
          "key": "prabhu joseph",
